description: Tomorrow is Christmas Eve! My HoneyDew this week is Rachael O'Brien! When you were 12 you probably hoped you got everything you wanted for Christmas...Rachael's dad told her he was dying. Rachael also shares a story about being bullied so badly as an adult that she went to a rehab facility to heal! Subscribe, download & review! I wish you all a very Merry Christmas, and a Happy Hanukkah!
